snippet: Tiger Woods said that his left Achilles’ tendon was not badly hurt and that he hoped he could still play next week at Bay Hill.
abstract: Tiger Woods says that his Achilles’ tendon is not badly hurt and he hopes to return to golf in a week's time.
lead_paragraph: Tiger Woods said that his left Achilles’ tendon was not badly hurt and that he hoped he could still play next week at Bay Hill.
